        configurationElementName - Element name of configuration
        optionalPackageName - package name different than default

                                                                               String[] customComponentScanningPaths,
                                                                               String... optionalPackageName)
        Create an IMutableConfiguration from a configuration element name, using also custom component scanning path to locate configuration class. If we can not create the object we return null except for the case of caller provided package name where we throw an exception.

        configurationElementName - Element name of configuration
        customComponentScanningPaths - paths where the custom components can be found
        optionalPackageName - package name different than default
        Returns:
        The configuration object, or null, if not found
